               <persName id="t18240603-113-person970">
                  Richard 
                  Edward Hopkins
               <interp inst="t18240603-113-person970" type="surname" value="Edward Hopkins"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18240603-113-person970" type="given" value="Richard"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18240603-113-person970" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , who keeps a sale shop. About half-past 8 o'clock (I was in the shop a minute or two before) I had gone into the room, and the door was partly shut. The jacket hung behind the door, and no one could get it without opening the door. I went to serve a customer, and this gentleman brought me the jacket.</p>
